data.description: Spacious town home in a most secluded neighborhood, near shopping, restaurants and Texas A&M University. Unique Italian porcelain tile flooring flows through the entry, living, kitchen and dining areas. Floor to ceiling windows look out to a masterfully crafted three season solarium with built in grill, sky-lights and access to master suite, living and dining rooms. The kitchen boasts of character with tile counters, sculpted stainless steel back splash, eating bar and breakfast area. The large master suite offers a walk-in closet through a unique armoire facade and features dual sinks and walk in shower in the master bath. Architectural features abound throughout the entire town home. For more information “Give Brandi a Ring!”
